        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This staff of magically hardened wood is topped with a silver sculpture depicting magical runic symbols. When used as a weapon, a <em>staff of power</em> is a <em>+2 greater striking staff</em>.</p>\n<p>Voluntarily destroying a <em>staff of power</em> unleashes an incredible blast of energy. When wielding the staff, you can Interact to break it. This releases a @Template[burst|distance:30] magical explosion centered on the staff. This deals @Damage[2d8[force]] damage per charge remaining in the staff (@Check[reflex|dc:40|basic]). You automatically critically fail your save. A creature reduced to 0 Hit Points by this damage dies instantly; this is a death effect.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells.</p>"
